      "widgets_values": [
        2112,
        1184,
        "{\"aspect_ratio\":\"9:16\",\"high_level_description\":\"A breathtaking, cinematic mirror-style selfie of a beautiful emo gothic girl riding on the back of a massive, hyper-realistic Tyrannosaurus Rex in a misty prehistoric jungle, captured with the ultra-high-fidelity quality of a Hasselblad medium format camera.\",\"compositional_deconstruction\":{\"background\":\"A lush, misty prehistoric jungle environment featuring towering ancient ferns, moss-draped cycads, and volumetric fog. The scene is illuminated by dramatic, dappled shafts of golden-hour sunlight piercing through the dense canopy, creating a complex chiaroscuro lighting setup with cool silvery ambient fill light clashing against warm amber highlights. Floating dust motes and humid atmospheric haze add depth, while the distant foliage melts into a creamy, shallow depth-of-field bokeh.\",\"elements\":[{\"type\":\"obj\",\"bbox\":[0.25,0.12,0.75,0.88],\"desc\":\"A beautiful emo gothic girl with porcelain-pale skin exhibiting advanced subsurface scattering, dark smoky eyeshadow, sharp winged eyeliner, and deep matte burgundy lipstick. Her raven-black hair is styled in a messy, textured half-updo with subtle hidden streaks of deep violet and crimson catching the light. She wears delicate silver facial piercings (septum ring, eyebrow stud), a black velvet choker with a teardrop obsidian pendant, and layered tarnished silver chain necklaces over a distressed, sheer black lace top. Her hand delicately holds a sleek iPhone adorned with subtle gothic aesthetic stickers, featuring chipped black nail polish and multiple ornate, intricate silver rings. Her expression is a captivating, slightly melancholic yet confident selfie gaze directed at the phone's camera lens.\"},{\"type\":\"obj\",\"bbox\":[0.05,0.45,0.95,0.98],\"desc\":\"A massive, hyper-realistic Tyrannosaurus Rex serving as the dynamic mount. The dinosaur features dark emerald and charcoal textured scales with intricate micro-details of wet, rugged reptilian skin, deep scars, and powerful, bulging musculature. Its head is turned slightly toward the camera lens, jaws slightly parted revealing formidable teeth, exuding a majestic, ancient, and powerful presence beneath the girl.\"},{\"type\":\"obj\",\"bbox\":[0,0,1,1],\"desc\":\"Photographic overlay and aesthetic: Shot on Hasselblad H6D-100c, 80mm f/2.8 lens, medium format photography. Features extraordinary dynamic range, micro-contrast, pin-sharp focus on the girl's eyes and the T-Rex's textured scales, brilliant specular highlights dancing on the iPhone screen and silver jewelry, and a cinematic, award-winning editorial photography aesthetic.\"}]}}",
